00:04:49.666 --> 00:04:51.767
Okay.

00:05:04.048 --> 00:05:06.283
Get out of here.

00:05:12.592 --> 00:05:14.727
- Good to go, boys.
- All right.

00:05:14.761 --> 00:05:16.829
<i>It's an original masonry house.</i>

00:05:16.897 --> 00:05:18.264
