over this green in here.

00:05:23.303 --> 00:05:26.305
- But I'll be here...
- Excuse me just a moment.

00:05:26.339 --> 00:05:28.140
Mrs. Hopewell, good morning.

00:05:28.174 --> 00:05:29.908
What are you doing here?

00:05:29.943 --> 00:05:32.210
